          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-938B420B-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-938B420B-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-938B420B-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-1" n="1">With half an Eye,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-2" n="2">Your riddle J spy</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-3" n="3">J observe your wicket,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-4" n="4">Hemm'd in by a Thicket,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-5" n="5">And whatever passes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-6" n="6">Js strain'd through Glasses,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-7" n="7">You're reported to dwell,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-8" n="8">Like a Monk in a Cell,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-9" n="9">You say you are quiet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-10" n="10">J flatly deny it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-11" n="11">Jt wanders about,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-12" n="12">Without stirring out,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-13" n="13">No passion so weak,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-14" n="14">But gives it a tweak,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-15" n="15">Love, joy, and Devotion,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-16" n="16">Set it always in motion,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-17" n="17">And as for y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Tragick,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-18" n="18">Effect of it's Magick,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-19" n="19">Which you say is to kill,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-20" n="20">And revive at it's Will,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-21" n="21">The Dead are all sound,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-22" n="22">And revive above ground,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-23" n="23">After all you have writ,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-24" n="24">Jt cannot be wit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-25" n="25">Which plainly does follow,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-26" n="26">Since it flies from Apollo,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-27" n="27">Jt's cowardis such,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-28" n="28">That it cries at a touch;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-29" n="29">Tis a perfect Milksop,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-30" n="30">Grows drunk with a drop,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-31" n="31">Another great fault,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-32" n="32">Jt cannot bear salt,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-33" n="33">And a hair can disarm,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B420B-line-34" n="34">Jt of every charm.</l>
          </lg>
